text: Aquarius Tour was a concert tour by American singer Tinashe. The tour strongly was about Tinashe's album, Aquarius, which released on October 7, 2014.https://thesource.com/2014/11/13/tinashe-gears-up-for-aquarius-tour The tour began on December 5, 2014 and ended March 17, 2015. The tour visited Europe, North America, Oceania, and Asia. == Shows == In total, there were 29 shows. 13 in Europe, 10 in North America, 5 in Oceania and 1 in Asia (specifically in the United Arab Emirates.) ==References== Category:Concert tours
title: Aquarius Tour
